
Mono Accessibility News

Copyright (C) 2008 Novell, Inc. (http://www.novell.com)

Version 0.9.1: The "Calculon" release
  * ToolStripSplitButton: Add support.
  * ToolStripDropDownButton: Fixed invoke behavior.
  * RadioButton: Listen for ISelectedProperty change event rather than
    ElementSelected event.
  * ListItem, Spinner: Only set Editable state if not ReadOnly.

Bugs fixed:
  * Selection implemented for ComboBox items
    https://bugzilla.novell.com/show_bug.cgi?id=449599

  * MessageBox should have a Dialog role not a Frame role
    https://bugzilla.novell.com/show_bug.cgi?id=444325

  * Handle basic AutomationEvents for StatusBarPanel
    https://bugzilla.novell.com/show_bug.cgi?id=449317

  * Change role of StatusBarPanel from Edit to Text.
    https://bugzilla.novell.com/show_bug.cgi?id=448465

  * Fix crash after clicking the text box inside of ComboBox
    https://bugzilla.novell.com/show_bug.cgi?id=456319

  * Fix Focused state of ComboBox
    https://bugzilla.novell.com/show_bug.cgi?id=456336

  * Properly set Name of LinkLabel controls
    https://bugzilla.novell.com/show_bug.cgi?id=447240

  * Properly set Role of LinkLabel controls
    https://bugzilla.novell.com/show_bug.cgi?id=447231

  * Fix accessibility bridge loading issue on openSUSE 11.1
    https://bugzilla.novell.com/show_bug.cgi?id=457787

Version 0.9: The "Zoidberg" release
  * Initial Release
